_sText:
Since you ppl want a more tactical map to knife your foes, i made one.

Its very dark on most of the map. As you can see there are little lighting. The middle has slow pulse lights that blink on and off. This map can prove whos the best at tactical knifing (using the dark ;P)

The 3rd screen is an overview of the map with the lights fully lit.
The 4th screen is an overview of the map with the lights going out.
